Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:45.46,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nigirishimeru kono te wo hirakeba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:53.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}furete shimau tou ni nageta kibou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:59.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}namida wo karashi mukau kono yami wo nuke
